Comment.Content: This is the first time I've read about sticky notes in VS2010. I guess they could be a useful feature for grueling debug sessions. BTW it's good to see some F# in action. I really look forward to getting into that.
Comment.TargetTitle: Yellow sticky notes for your watched variables in the new VS 2010
